"Ain't she sweet"
Sale By Set Date: Monday 16th December at 5pm (unless sold prior)
A touch of history close to everything Dandenong offers exists in this huge allotment of 729m2 (approx.). Ideal for the astute developer, this home presents a wonderful opportunity for all who view it.
Step into a dream with beautiful ceiling roses, ornate cornices and lovely touches throughout, as this home presents a bygone era with high ceilings and large blocks. With other developments close by, this property lends itself to the building of townhouses or units (STCA).
The home itself has a large kitchen and various living areas, ducted heating and central cooling, perfect to live in already or rent out while planning for a development!
Close to transport, schools, parks and Dandenong Central, this home represents a plethora of possibilities.
Inspections by appointment only.

Description:
TOWNHOUSE WITH A SEPARATE DRIVEWAY!
Situated in a quiet street, this double story dwelling in a highly desirable location certainly going to attract your attention. Ground floor comprises spacious lounge separated from kitchen and dining, powder room and a spacious backyard. Upper floor comprises spacious 3bedrooms, master bedroom with walk in robes, tiles to the wet areas. One bedroom comprises balcony with street view. Lockable garage and easy maintenance backyard tick the rest of boxes. As the heading says having a separate driveway is a huge bonus. Location speaks itself within minutes away from hemming street shopping precinct, railway station, medical center and Dandenong west primary school. Ideal as an entry level home for a first home buyer, downsizer or as an investment property. Currently let to great tenants returning $1521pcm on a monthly tenancy. With a bit of imagination and tender loving care, this home can be brought to former glory with huge potential.
Inspection is highly recommended.

Description:
Approved Plans and Permits for 2 Townhouses
Resonating with builders and developers keen to take on their next project, this brilliantly located weatherboard residence comes complete with plans and permits in place for two townhouses, each encompassing three bedrooms, spacious kitchen, living and dining domains along with garage parking.
Adorned with magnificent high ceilings and modern floorboards, the existing home is currently tenanted and offers three bedrooms accompanied by an L-shaped lounge and dining, separate kitchen with stainless steel appliances and Chef dishwasher, family bathroom with toilet plus a laundry and rear yard.
Situated in a dream location that's brilliantly connected to a wide range of amenities and offers the convenience of walking distance to Yarraman Oaks Primary, Dandenong High School and Yarraman Train Station, close to shops, parkland, South Eastern Private Hospital plus EastLink and Monash Freeway access.

Description:
Another one SOLD by the BABET BROTHERS!
Another one SOLD by the BABET BROTHERS!
Please follow us on Facebook, Instagram and YouTube for regular fresh content search "Babet Brothers Real Estate".
Ladies and Gentleman, we have something special for you today. Suitable for both owner occupiers and investors this lovely fully renovated apartment is simply perfect. Situated in an ideal location and close to absolutely everything that Dandenong has to offer you are sure to be impressed. Within easy walking distance to Chisholm TAFE, Dandenong Hospital, Dandenong Plaza Shopping Centre, Dandenong market and within a short drive to the Dandenong train station and Monash Freeway entrance.
The apartment building only features a total of 7 apartments unlike some other buildings in the area. Situated in a quite street and with its own off street parking spot this one is not to be missed.
Stepping into the apartment will truly amaze, it is extremely spacious compared to others in this area and is flooded with natural light. The living area is of ample size and features more than enough room for couches, TV cabinet, coffee table, kitchen table etc. The kitchen itself is tasteful, functional and modern with stainless steel appliances throughout and features ample storage space.
The main bathroom of the home features a tub, rarely seen in apartments and is also tastefully renovated.
The two bedrooms of the apartment are large and have more than enough room for a kingsize bed as well as bed side tables. They feature ample storage and have built in robes.
The apartment has high quality floor tiles, air conditioning/heating and gorgeous views from the balcony of the Dandenong Ranges mountains.
The location of the apartment is excellent with public transport meters from the front door. This is sure to sell very quickly.
Don't miss out! Contact the Babet Brothers today to avoid disappointment!

Description:
Brand New, Just For You...
A home for those that expect nothing less than the best, 24 Wilma Avenue embodies premium family living at its finest. Generously proportioned, elegantly styled this grand family home will leave you breathless.
This contemporary house is your chance to own and enjoy everything brand new and just for you. Positioned in the heart of thriving Dandenong, this premium location offers both primary and secondary schools within less than 1km, convenient shopping at Dandenong Markets and Plaza, a selection of local parks and reserves as well as easy transport options with nearby bus services, Merinda And Dandenong Train Station, Princes Highway.
The home's commanding facade greets guests and residents with a hint of the luxury to follow. Inside continues to deliver with high ceilings, bright interiors and quality throughout. On the ground floor, walk in from the front door into the formal lounge and study. A Second open plan living and dining area connects with the private courtyard. The Kitchen beams brightly with white finishes, comprises of a 5-burner gas cooktop, under bench oven, soft close drawers and white cabinetry and complemented by stone benches and mosaic tiled splashback. Master bedroom with full Ensuite and Walk in robe complete the downstairs layout whilst upstairs accommodates three bedrooms with built in robes, a central bathroom, retreat area.
This home truly has everything you could want and a list of extras so long you need to see it to truly appreciate it all. Ducted heating and Evaporative cooling offer instant comfort and a double garage adds secure parking to the home. Completed with landscaping, the outdoor space also includes a patio for outdoor dining, water tank and double garage.
Close to Dandenong West Primary School, Greaves Reserve, Eastlink, the Monash Freeway and so much more!
Be sure to inspect without delay and avoid missing out.

Description:
SUPERB HOME WITH NO BODY CORP!
Ray White Dandenong proudly presents this wonderful unit, set in a coveted location which presents a fantastic opportunity for first home buyers, astute investors, growing families and those looking to downsize. Immaculately presented, this lovely family residence requires no work and is ready for you to move right in!
Offering 3 good sized bedrooms, a lovely living area which is adjacent to the delightful kitchen equipped with gas cooking and abundance of cupboard space. The main fully renovated bathroom and laundry make up the interior of this lovely home.
Features of this home include: 2 Split systems, air conditioner ,new floor boards, downlights, spacious backyard, garden shed and much more.
Located within a stones-throw away from Dandenong South Primary School, Dandenong Station, Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink, Dandenong Creek walking trail, public transport and recreational facilities. This home is all but ready for you to make it your own.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!
*PHOTO I.D. REQUIRED UPON INSPECTION*

Description:
Two Homes on 777m2
A Dandenong Central location, only a short walk to St John's College, St Mary's and the city centre on a generous 777m2 of land with development potential and lots of options!
The property accommodates an older style three bedroom home with double garage and a two bedroom brick veneer unit with lock up garage and secure backyard at the rear.
Lots of option:
1) Ideal for large, extended family
2) Rent out both dwellings
3) Knock down home and build two units at the front (STCA)
This property represents a great opportunity to secure a great location with potential to redevelop (STCA).
YOU'RE ON A WINNER!

Description:
A ideal start or unbeatable investment!
Located in a highly desirable pocket of Dandenong, this gorgeous townhouse is an ideal step into the property market for first home owners, down-sizers & investor's alike, boasting low maintenance living & close to all amenities.
Comprising of a user-friendly floor plan, two bedrooms with ceiling fans, one bathroom with shower & tub, large living area, modern kitchen with gas cooktop & oven, plenty of benchtop & cabinet space as well as a separate meals area, low maintenance courtyard with decking & a generously sized laundry.
You will be delighted by the serenity knowing that you're only moments away from Primary and Secondary Schools, bus stops, Short drive to Dandenong Shopping Centre, Market and Hospital,. Also offers you easy access to M1, East link, Princes Hwy and other major roads. Arrange to inspect before it is too late!
Note to investors: this property is on fixed term tenancy $1434 pcm (Approx.), tenancy is until Feb 2020.

Description:
Walk to Train Station
You won't need a car when you buy this neat and spacious ground floor apartment which is only one of 10 on the block with its own carport on Title and conveniently located under 15 minutes walk to train station, Dandenong Plaza, Market, High School and many other central facilities.
It offers a large lounge huge master bedroom plus second bedroom with built in robes, combined bathroom/laundry, separate toilet and kitchen with meals area and gas cooking.
Other extras include extensive tiling, bright interior and front and rear security doors.
POSITION MATTERS!
